application.news

Class Article

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.news.Article

  • public class Article
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents an article. An article is formed by: - A title - A subtitle - An Image - HTML text for the abstract - HTML text for the body - An article could be mark as deleted (only administrator users can see an modify it) - An article belong to one category
    Author:
    agonzalez
